lr4ranger

This package includes a C library to communicate with the Porcupine LR4
Laser Rangefinder.  Sample programs in C and Python are included.

Platforms Tested
----------------
- Mac OS X (10.9.1)
- Linux (CentOS, Raspbian)

Prerequisites
-------------
- C compiler
- The libusb-1.0 library and header files

Build
-----
type 'make'

Demo
----
- src/ranger_test is a C application that does a single range test
- demo/lr4ranger.py is a simple python script

Author
------
